CatDescriptText: Cutline of image published in Pittsburgh Courier newspaper, August 11, 1956, pg. A15, reads: "Time Out...was taken between dance sets to...[illegible]...visitors and friends at the various tables. Enjoying each other's company are Mrs. James Haney, widow of one of the pioneer Frogs...[illegible]...and her husband of Cleveland; Mrs. Christopher Jefferies...[illegible]...Dr. Jeffries who is talking with Dr. J....[illegible]..."
TitMainTitle: Men and women seated at "old timers" table, including Mrs. James Haney, Mrs. and Dr. Christopher Jefferies, in ballroom Penn-Sheraton Hotel, for FROGS formal
